description.en:
OryxCoin is P2P service providing crypto-currency online banking marketplace. OryxCoin Blockchain works as a self-regulated online network, which is governed by decentralised system algorithms, powered by a virtual electrical grid of Masternode CPUs. OryxCoin enables crypto-currency online banking services, including payment services in cash-able finite electronic numbers.

Oryx is a project aimed at revolutionizing the concept of Venture Capital by making it decentralized by distributing it on its patented Blockchain. OryxCoin is a revolutionary utility cryptocurrency that gives you full control and freedom. It can expand the potential of what you can do in this modern digital world.
